{"tid":1738620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動唔係聽朝先郁手架！","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:26:43.000Z","uid":113932,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c97f47753b781b22f556cf9c1fd0ab5cf23918bb","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"根據我既經驗，第二朝先行動多數唔work<br />\n一來香港人最鍾意遲到，約6:30就7:30先見人<br />\n到時D人都上晒車番晒工，根本阻唔到<br />\n<br />\n二來朝早先set RB班廢老藍絲一定會出嚟阻頭阻勢，又冇夜色掩護萬一有狗離到好難走<br />\n<br />\n三來朝早塞鐵其實每個站阻得十幾分鐘，D港豬真係想番都會番到，最多遲個幾兩個鐘，效用不大<br />\n<br />\n建議夜晚set定D不能輕易移走既RB先<br />\n第二朝再快閃各區用雜物/鐵釘擋路<br />\n至於黨鐵，最好當然係夜晚爆鐵<br />\n直接令佢第二日閂站，搞到班港豬想番都番唔到<br />\n塞鐵只係爆鐵不成功後備方案<br />\n不過都要小心比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n記住，唔好係連登/公海傾行動詳情！！！<br />\n搵信得過既人組隊係tg傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝各位今晚旅途愉快"},{"pid":"51545e796e6b91ced80dfcce27317b982263c00e","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"撞行動po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca8bc13a61f9352d0d8392e8cb9cebe6203d06d","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"364443bcf850cf35d5c99dbaabd010b589d1e892","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"809d5a8fbe7451df9f5f05da5309a533c25c2068","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"20a4f6c85b07d9e174524ac7a3c17280b952420d","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"19d85983ca9443db88913ee5be7124d548955e1d","tid":1738620,"uid":113932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"b7685e90c4208eabb93b6cd41c3f0510887ef678","ti